== Availability ==
The standard Susanowa is available at the Yaki shipyard in Senator's Badlands. The variants must be captured by forcing the pilots to bail.
== Suggested Roles==
With performance characteristics similar to the [[Mamba]], the Susanowa is an effective wingman or swarm fighter although the low shielding makes it vulnerable to attrition.  The Prototype variant is the fastest ship in the universe that's capable of mounting the powerful Plasma Burst Generator, but the small cargo space when compared to the Mamba restrict it to be a carrier-based fighter only.

